            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>CVS保健(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CVS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CVS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CVS-US</a>)截至台北時間31日21:30股價上漲3.21美元，報65.51美元，漲幅5.15%，成交量775,753（股），盤中最高價65.51美元、最低價65.51美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.21%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.75%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.15%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.83%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>CVS保健(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CVS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CVS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CVS-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+2%</li> <li>近 1 月：-9.68%</li> <li>近 3 月：-6.61%</li> <li>近 6 月：+9.64%</li> <li>今年以來：+38.78%</li></ul></section></main>",
